Makes sense. I will say we definitely need to sort through some record remapping bugs and as a team first before like this one which I think Matt ran into with Velocity as well https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05BJCNKZAM/p1749843566997479?thread_ts=1749836132.724989&cid=C05BJCNKZAM
thanks for added context - I'm scheduled to chat with the design team Monday morning to get this to dev-ready
I'd estimate a week or so to turn those around depending on what else is on the team's plate, but we'll share the designs back for some feedback when ready
